Class SimpleStyleableStringProperty

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Observable, Property<String>, ReadOnlyProperty<String>, ObservableObjectValue<String>, ObservableStringValue, ObservableValue<String>, WritableObjectValue<String>, WritableStringValue, WritableValue<String>, StyleableProperty<String>
public class SimpleStyleableStringProperty extends StyleableStringProperty
This class extends SimpleStringProperty and provides a full implementation of a StyleableProperty. This class is used to make a StringProperty, that would otherwise be implemented as a SimpleStringProperty, styleable by CSS.
Since:
JavaFX 8.0
